---
title: "Sequence Diagram: Video Streaming Service"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE   as Frontend<br/>(React/Ionic)
    participant SS   as StreamService<br/>(port 8003)
    participant JWT  as JWTHandler<br/>(Infra/Security)
    participant OCV  as OpenCV Capture<br/>(Infra)
    participant WSM  as WebSocket Manager<br/>(Infra)
    participant FEED as Camera Feed<br/>(RTSP/HTTP)
    participant DB   as PostgreSQL

    Note over User,DB: ── START STREAM ────────────────────────────────────────

    User ->> FE  : Click "Watch Live Stream" for camera
    activate FE
    FE   ->> SS  : POST /api/v1/streams/start<br/>Authorization: Bearer <token><br/>{ camera_id, stream_url, config }
    activate SS
    SS   ->> JWT : verify_token(token, "access")
    activate JWT
    JWT -->> SS  : { user_id }
    deactivate JWT

    SS   ->> DB  : SELECT session WHERE camera_id=?<br/>AND status IN ('active','connecting')
    activate DB
    DB  -->> SS  : Session | None
    deactivate DB

    alt Session already ACTIVE
        SS  -->> FE  : 200 { ws_url, is_new: false }
    else No active session → start new
        SS   ->> DB  : INSERT INTO stream_sessions<br/>(camera_id, status='pending', fps)
        activate DB
        DB  -->> SS  : session_id
        deactivate DB

        SS   ->> OCV : VideoCapture(stream_url)
        activate OCV
        OCV  ->> FEED : Connect (RTSP handshake / HTTP GET)
        activate FEED
        FEED -->> OCV : Stream established
        deactivate FEED
        OCV -->> SS  : capture_handle
        deactivate OCV

        SS   ->> DB  : UPDATE status='active', started_at=NOW()
        activate DB
        DB  -->> SS  : OK
        deactivate DB
        SS   ->> WSM : register_stream(camera_id, capture_handle)
        activate WSM
        WSM -->> SS  : OK
        deactivate WSM
        SS  -->> FE  : 200 { ws_url: "/ws/stream/{camera_id}", is_new: true }
    end
    deactivate SS

    Note over User,DB: ── WEBSOCKET FRAME DELIVERY ─────────────────────────────

    FE   ->> SS  : WS CONNECT /ws/stream/{camera_id}?token=<access_token>
    activate SS
    SS   ->> JWT : verify_token(token, "access")
    activate JWT
    JWT -->> SS  : { user_id }
    deactivate JWT
    SS   ->> WSM : add_client(camera_id, ws_connection)
    activate WSM
    WSM -->> SS  : OK
    deactivate WSM
    SS  -->> FE  : WS OPEN (101 Switching Protocols)
    FE  -->> User : Show live video player

    loop Every frame at configured FPS (~15fps)
        SS   ->> OCV : cap.read()
        activate OCV
        OCV -->> SS  : BGR numpy frame
        deactivate OCV
        SS   ->> SS  : cv2.imencode('.jpg', frame, quality=80)<br/>→ JPEG bytes
        SS   ->> DB  : UPDATE last_frame_at = NOW()
        SS  -->> FE  : WS BINARY <JPEG frame bytes>
        FE  -->> User : Render frame on canvas element
    end

    Note over User,DB: ── STOP STREAM ─────────────────────────────────────────

    User ->> FE  : Close stream view
    FE   ->> SS  : WS CLOSE (1000 Normal)
    SS   ->> WSM : remove_client(camera_id, ws_connection)
    activate WSM
    WSM -->> SS  : clients_remaining = 0
    deactivate WSM
    SS  -->> FE  : WS CLOSED
    deactivate SS

    FE   ->> SS  : POST /api/v1/streams/stop { camera_id }
    activate SS
    SS   ->> OCV : cap.release()
    SS   ->> WSM : close_all_clients(camera_id)
    activate WSM
    WSM -->> SS  : OK
    deactivate WSM
    SS   ->> DB  : UPDATE stream_sessions<br/>SET status='stopped', stopped_at=NOW()
    activate DB
    DB  -->> SS  : OK
    deactivate DB
    SS  -->> FE  : 200 { status: "stopped", stopped_at }
    deactivate SS
    FE  -->> User : "Stream ended"
    deactivate FE
